Upgrade your college football experience with Superfan Sports for College Football! Lightning fast updates, immersive play-by-play, complete player & team stats, odds, news, standings, & much more. Our clean & intuitive design is lightweight, fast, and fully customizable. Enjoy every NCAA college football game - without the clutter.

• Live college football scores and real-time boxscore stats keep you in the action.
• Lightning-fast updates, including every play of every FBS football game.
• Immediate game alerts for scores, close games, overtime, and more!
• Game previews with detailed team stat matchups for all FBS & FCS games.
• Full game lines including odds for the first half and second half.
• Betting trends with outcomes in head-to-head games & records against the spread.
• Full college football conference standings, AP Top 25 rankings, college football playoff (CFP) rankings, and more.
• Season stat leaders for players and teams.
• TV listings for all games.
• Customize your schedule! Filter by team, conference or rankings.
• Access the latest football news for the NCAA and your favorite college teams on the go.
• Season stats for teams and players.
• No internet connection? No problem! The full schedule is available offline.
• Includes the entire 2024 NCAA college football season schedule

NCAA Bowl games will be added as scheduled, including the college football playoffs.
